title: Posole with Garnishes
summary: Posole with Garnishes is a gluten free and vegetarian main course. This recipe makes 4 servings with 391 calories, 15g of protein, and 15g of fat each. For $3.52 per serving, this recipe covers 37% of your daily requirements of vitamins and minerals. Not a lot of people made this recipe, and 2 would say it hit the spot. A mixture of jalapeno pepper, garlic cloves, bay leaves, and a handful of other ingredients are all it takes to make this recipe so scrumptious. To use up the avocado you could follow this main course with the chocolate avocado mousse | quick dark chocolate avocado mousse as a dessert. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes around 45 minutes. All things considered, we decided this recipe deserves a spoonacular score of 92%. This score is awesome. Try Sriracha Bloody Mary & having fun with garnishes, Roasted Garlic Guacamole with Help-Yourself Garnishes, and Spiralized Garnishes & a Jalapeno-Cilantro Green Juice for similar recipes.
